title: 591. 10 Takeaways from Week 3
itunes:title: 591. 10 Takeaways from Week 3
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Rhett Lewis look back at the weekend and pick ten storylines that stood out from Week 3 of the NFL season. To start off, the guys discuss QB Russell Wilson and how he erases mistakes for the Seahawks (:54). Next, the duo focus on QB Aaron Rodgers and how he makes everyone around him better (4:19). Later, the pair analyze how the Patriots are chameleons (18:17). To wrap up the show, DJ and Rhett touch on the Bears making a QB change to Nick Foles (30:44). All that and more in this packed episode.
